# Hololand Central Environment Variables

# Admin Wallet Addresses (comma-separated, lowercase)
# These wallets will have access to the admin panel via the secret Infinity Shop trigger
# To access: Click Brittney hologram 5 times within 3 seconds in Infinity Shop
VITE_ADMIN_WALLETS=0x1234567890123456789012345678901234567890,0xabcdefabcdefabcdefabcdefabcdefabcdefabcd

# Example configuration:
# VITE_ADMIN_WALLETS=0xYourWalletAddress1,0xYourWalletAddress2

# Note: Addresses should be:
# - Ethereum wallet addresses (42 characters starting with 0x)
# - Comma-separated without spaces
# - Lowercase (the system will normalize them)
